query:
insert into nft_price_history (
                source, 
                source_type, 
                ts, 
                price,
                price_token, 
                nft,
                usd_price,
                collection
            )
            select
                unnest($1::varchar[]),
                unnest($2::nft_price_source[]),
                unnest($3::timestamp[]),
                unnest($4::numeric[]),
                unnest($5::varchar[]),
                unnest($6::varchar[]),
                unnest($7::numeric[]),
                unnest($8::varchar[])
